    "Accidents involving AI systems often occur in edge cases, so extensive testing of all possible scenarios becomes crucial for detecting and mitigating potential risks.",
    "69 When assessing legitimate safety expectations in product liability, the relevant moment is when the product was put into circulation, not the expectations that pertained to when the damage occurred.",
    "By extension, a product is not considered defective for the mere reason that a better product is subsequently put into circulation.",
